            <string language="sl">Žuželke in druge majhne živali brez okostja</string>
            <string language="en">Insects and other small animals without skeleton</string>

            <string language="x-mt-es">Insectos y otros animales pequeños sin el 
esqueleto</string>
          </title>
          <language>sl</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Gradivo je izdelano v obliki določevalnih ključev za prepoznavanje manjših živali, ki živijo v zemlji, pod drevesno skorjo, na cvetovih in steblih rastlin, pod kamenjem, … Razvija sposobnost natančnega opazovanje živih bitij in usmerja k uporabi literature.</string>
            <string language="en">Presentation of many insects (fly, spider, caterpillar, dragonfly, bee) and other small animals - their main properties, how to recognize them, special organs, ...</string>
          </description>

          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Darstellung vieler Insekte (Fliege, Spinne, 
Gleiskettenfahrzeug, Libelle, Biene) und anderer kleiner Tiere - ihre 
Haupteigenschaften, wie man sie, spezielle Organe... erkennt</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Présentation de beaucoup d'insectes (mouche, 
araignée, chenille, libellule, abeille) et d'autres petits animaux - 
leurs propriétés principales, comment les identifier, organes 
spéciaux...</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Apresentação de muitos insetos (mosca, aranha, 
lagarta, libélula, abelha) e de outros animais pequenos - suas 
propriedades principais, como reconhecê-los, órgãos especiais...</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Presentazione di molti insetti (mosca, ragno, 
trattore a cingoli, libellula, ape) e di altri piccoli animali - le 
loro proprietà principali, come riconoscerli, organi speciali...</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Παρουσίαση πολλών εντόμων (μύγα, αράχνη, κάμπια, 
λιβελλούλη, μέλισσα) και άλλων μικρών ζώων - οι βασικές 
ιδιότητές τους, πώς να τους αναγνωρίσει, ειδικά όργανα...</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Presentación de muchos insectos (mosca, araña, 
oruga, libélula, abeja) y de otros animales pequeños - sus 
características principales, cómo reconocerlos, órganos 
especiales...</string>
